  "content": {
    "visible_text": "Becoming the Change Part II December 24, 2025 Becoming the Change December 4, 2025 30 Years of Service August 19, 2025 Sinking Roots December 30, 2024 Embrace the Change December 11, 2024 Burner Dojo in Black Rock City 2022 :: 5:00 & Enigma August 16, 2022 Find Quantum on the Playa at 5:00 & E, Black Rock City 2022! Every Community Needs a Dojo December 28, 2021 On Resilience: Emerging from the pandemic stronger than we were before June 12, 2021 The Dragon and Tiger Rooms, 2015–2020 December 29, 2020 The Denny Dojo and Quantum SF, 2007-2015 December 16, 2020 The Aurora Dojo: North Seattle, 2000–2007 November 25, 2020 The Quantum Leap 2020! November 17, 2020 1 2 3 Next » Reviews Facebook Community Dojo Quantum Martial Arts is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit in the State of California, and we thrive on the generosity of people like you. All donations are tax-deductible. Quantum’s tax ID number is 26-1534597. No donation is too small, or too large. Whether it’s $20 or $20,000, every cent will be hugely appreciated and put to good use. Support Our Kids Donate now to support our youth scholarship program which allows families in need to train at reduced cost. We believe investment in our community involves investing in our youth. Our Sister Schools Our Seattle Dojo has served thousands of students since opening on Capitol Hill in 1995, and currently offers youth and adult classes in the Central District. Our Portland Dojo was established in 2020, and currently offers youth and adult classes in Southeast Portland. A WordPress.com Website .",
